# PWA Screenshot Placeholders

This directory should contain PWA screenshots for the manifest.json.

## Required Screenshots

### Desktop (form_factor: "wide")
- desktop-home.png (1920x1080) - Home page showing recent shows and statistics
- desktop-setlist.png (1920x1080) - Show setlist detail view

### Mobile (form_factor: "narrow")
- mobile-home.png (750x1334) - Mobile home view
- mobile-songs.png (750x1334) - Song database on mobile

## How to Generate

1. Run the dev server: `npm run dev`
2. Use Chrome DevTools device emulator for mobile sizes
3. Take screenshots at the specified dimensions
4. Save as PNG files in this directory

## Notes

- Screenshots improve PWA install experience
- Desktop screenshots appear in the "Install" dialog on Chrome/Edge
- Mobile screenshots appear in app stores when PWA is distributed
